  ;; ── Connections / Net labels ──────────────────────────────────────

  ;; I2C bus: PB6 (SCL) → U2.SCL, U9.SCL
  ;;           PB7 (SDA) → U2.SDA, U9.SDA

  ;; MUX select: PA8→S0, PA9→S1, PA10→S2, PB9→S3
  ;; MUX enable: PA4 (active low) → U3.EN
  ;; MUX common → U2.A0 (ADS1115 single-ended input)

  ;; Moisture oscillators: U4.OUT→PC6, U5.OUT→PC7, U6.OUT→PC8

  ;; DS18B20: PC13 (data, open-drain), PA12 (power, push-pull)

  ;; VBAT sense: PB11 ← voltage divider on supercap

  ;; 1-Wire: PC13 ← DS18B20 data (with 4.7kΩ pullup)

  ;; Status LEDs: PB2 (green), PB3 (red)

)